 out so I played 2hours and was complete and really annoyed and let down.£14.99 + 2hours = Annoyed.The price being asked is not worth the time it needs.  As soon as the game goes on sale for below 50% then buy it instantly.  If you see a 75% off sale on this game, you would be a fool to miss it, but right now full price no!"
